# GUI
plasma-desktop - Core desktop
sddm - More mature than plasma-login-manager (systemctl enable --now sddm)
sddm-kcm - KDE themes and integrations with SDDM (Make sure to setup /etc/sddm.conf.d/EpsilonOS.conf)
plasma-nm - Network Manager SysTray (systemctl enable --now NetworkManager) iwd exists but wpa_supplicant is just easier.
plasma-pa - Audio SysTray
pipewire-pulse - Pipewire and PulseAudio replacement (systemctl enable --now --user pipewire pipewire-pulse)
wireplumber - Session manager for Pipewire (systemctl enable --now --user wireplumber)
kscreen - Display settings panel
powerdevil - Power profiles SysTray
power-profiles-daemon - Backend for powerdevil (systemctl enable --now power-profiles-daemon)
bluedevil - Bluetooth SysTray. Includes bluez (systemctl enable --now bluetooth)
dolphin - File manager (not included by default)
spectacle - Screenshot utility
alacritty - Terminal emulator
firefox - Web browser

